<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200724/aca0b2d32a4a4eeab31b63346c998966.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">暗香横斜 59.5X29 CM</span></img></p>
